{
  "stem": "9245.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's-- I-- I barely scratched the surface of what I was telling.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, it's so many things that happened, while-- human stories and unhuman stories.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "By the way, the-- the person, the farmer, that saved us, right after we escaped the ghetto, I-- I think of him an-- a-- a long-- an-- an awful many times, because he was a very, very noble human being.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And for-- he paid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He and his wife and his son and daughter-in-law and the children paid with his life.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "His Ukrainian brethren came and-- and killed them and burned down his house for helping Jews.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There's the-- that's the inhuman part.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The human part, it was of-- one person that helped out Jews.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the reason I am doing it-- this is my second tape.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I did one tape in 1983.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I feel that each and every one of us survivors has a tremendous mission to accomplish of telling the story of our survival.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because in view of the fact of what's going on, with the people that are coming out, the reformists, saying that it's a hoax, it's not happen, we are the witnesses.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We lived through it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we know what happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I talk to my friends, survivors.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I urge them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Many of them cannot talk about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And to tell you the truth, I can see their point of-- What they went through, in concentration camps, does not compare, no way, to-- to my life.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Even though of I-- what I went through, having hunger and having-- and-- and being in cold and-- and-- and-- and being so sick, I-- I was running from death.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I wasn't facing death.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I felt that we-- we still contributed something by fighting the Germans and doing some damage to them.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
